  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 17.26,
      "time_str": "00:17.260",
      "text": "以前我总觉得 情歌都是一样",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 24.22,
      "time_str": "00:24.220",
      "text": "总是用重复的伎俩 来骗你的感伤",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 32.189,
      "time_str": "00:32.189",
      "text": "试着对你放手以后",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.14,
      "time_str": "00:36.140",
      "text": "我才慢慢学会了欣赏",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.28,
      "time_str": "00:40.280",
      "text": "为什么会有那首说谎",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.28,
      "time_str": "00:44.280",
      "text": "十年后谁还不见不散",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.15,
      "time_str": "00:50.150",
      "text": "我已经好久好久不听情歌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 54.17,
      "time_str": "00:54.170",
      "text": "因为有太多太多的不快乐",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 58.37,
      "time_str": "00:58.370",
      "text": "可是旋律一直残忍的在我耳边",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 62.75,
      "time_str": "01:02.750",
      "text": "循环着我对你的不舍",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 66.27,
      "time_str": "01:06.270",
      "text": "我以为以后以后不听情歌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 70.28,
      "time_str": "01:10.280",
      "text": "就不会想你想得那么曲折",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 74.43,
      "time_str": "01:14.430",
      "text": "可连安静都像闹钟",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.0,
      "time_str": "01:17.000",
      "text": "提醒着你不是我的",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 99.31,
      "time_str": "01:39.310",
      "text": "有谁能够体会 我现在的难受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 106.229,
      "time_str": "01:46.229",
      "text": "和你纠缠了那么久 你牵了他的手",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 114.22,
      "time_str": "01:54.220",
      "text": "假装着不去问候",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 118.289,
      "time_str": "01:58.289",
      "text": "假装只是你普通朋友",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 122.3,
      "time_str": "02:02.300",
      "text": "我闹够了没有 哪一天",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 126.27,
